quran[128]{c,v,t}:
  16,1,"Likhuwa lia Nyasaye liloola butswa, kho mulaliyungubasia tawe. Obutswenufu nobubwe, ne ali hekulu muno wa akabamutsokaasinjia ninako."
  16,2,"Yeshinjia abalaika nende obufimbuli, khubuchami bubwe khu ulia owayenya mubasumba bebe, mbu: “Kanyilisie (Abandu) mbu abulaho nyasaye wundi owulali Esie tawe, kho murie esie.”"
  16,3,"Yaloonga likulu nende eshialo khubwatoto, ali hekulu muno wa ebiabamutsokasinjia ninabio."
  16,4,"Yaloonga Omundu okhurulana nende indonyande yamatsi kolwibulo, mana naye naba omuyingasi owa habulafu."
  16,5,"Ne yaloonga tsisolo, mwetso munyoolangamwo obutundumu nende obukhoonyi, ne etsindi mutsilitsanga."
  16,6,"Ne mulolanga obulayi olwa mutsikalusinjia ingolobe nende shingala mutsiyilanga mushiayo itsuli."
  16,7,"Ne tsibachinjilanga emisiko chienyu okhula mutsingongo tsiamulakholelemwo tawe halali nimunyakhane muno. Toto Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi ni Omuholo muno, Owetsimbabaasi."
  16,8,"Nende tsifarasi, nende tsinyumbu nende tsipunda, mutsininenjekhwo, ne tsibe oburone (bwenyu), ne aloonganga ebia mulamanyile tawe."
  16,9,"Ne ni khu Nyasaye okhwechesia Injila (ili habwene), ne tsiliwo etsindi tsilali habwene tawe. Ne yenyanga, toto yakhabalunjisiye mweesi."
  16,10,"Ye niye ubeshilinjia amatsi okhurula mwikulu, khuko munyoolanga kokhunywa, nende emimela chiamulisinjia ebiayo."
  16,11,"Ne khuko abamesilinjia ebirache, nende zaituni, nende emitende, nende emizabibu nende buli ebiamo. Toto mwako kalimwo ameeko khubandu baparanga."
  16,12,"Ne yabaanguyilia eshilo nende eshitere, eliuba nende omwesi, nende tsing’ining’ini tsioosi tsianguyibwa khubunyali bubwe. Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko khubandu bekhonyelanga obwongo."
  16,13,"Nende bilia ebiayabalonjera khushialo ebiobukoondo bwaukhane. Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko khubandu betsulilanga."
  16,14,"Niye wabaanguyisilia inyanza mbu khomunyoole okhuliamwo inyama indorotoro inzelemu, ne murusinjiamwo ebirone bia mwifwalanga, ne olola shinga ebininungwamwo shingala bikhalakaninjiamwo, mbu khomunyoole tsimbabaasi tsitsie, ne khomunyoole okhumupila orio."
  16,15,"Ne nara khushialo tsingulu mbu (eshialo) shilabeyabeya ninanyu tawe, nende emialo nende tsinjila; khomunyoole okhulunjkha."
  16,16,"Ne yaraho ebimanyisio bindi. Ne beelunjisinjia injila okhwikhonyela tsing’ining’ini."
  16,17,"Mbu ulia uloonganga yakhaba shiabulala nende ulia ulaalonganga tawe? Koo, shimwitsulilanga tawe?"
  16,18,"Ne kata nimubala emikabo chia Nyasaye (khwinywe), shimwakhachimala tawe. Toto Nyasaye niwobulesheli po, owetsimbabaasi muno."
  16,19,"Ne Nyasaye amanyile kamufisanga nende akamuretsanga habulafu."
  16,20,"Ne balia ababalaamanga abalali Nyasaye tawe, shibaloonganga shiosishiosi tawe halali bo balongungwa."
  16,21,"Ni abafuu, shinabalamu tawe, ne bakorerwe mbu balilamusibwa lina."
  16,22,"Nyasaye wenyu ni Nyasaye mulala. Ne balia abalasuubilanga mwikulu tawe emioyo chiabu chikhayanga, nabo bakholanga obufuru."
  16,23,"Toto bwene Nyasaye yamanya akabafisanga nende akabaretsanga habulafu. Toto ye shiyachama abakholanga obufuru tawe."
  16,24,"Ne nibarebwa mbu: “Nishina shia Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi yeshiye?” Nibaboola mbu: “Ni tsingano tsiobubeyi tsia abandu bakhale sa.”"
  16,25,"Kho bachinge emisiko chiabu emilamba inyanga yeyindukho, nende emisiko chia balia ababakosinjia khukhubula obumanyi. Koo, ni amabii kali karie kano kabachinganga!"
  16,26,"Toto balia abali imbeli wabu bakhola ebifwanga, mana Nyasaye naresia amatililo ketsinzu tsiabu mana ebitsafu nibibakwakho okhurulila hekulu, mana eshinyasio nishibetsela munjila yabalamanyile tawe."
  16,27,"Mana khandi inyanga yeyindukho alibafimbia omurwe, ne aliboola mbu: “Bali hena balia abamwanzokasinjia ninabo, abachilanga nimuyingana?” Balia abahebwa obumanyi baliboola mbu: “Toto isoni nende amasila nyanga yino biloolela Abakhayi.”"
  16,28,"Balia aba abamalaika bafwisinjia nibekholeele tsimbi! Mana balilekhulila Nyasaye (okhubera lifwa libolere baliboola mbu): “Sikhwakholanga obwononi bwosibwosi tawe.” (Abamalaika balibakalusia mbu): “Hee toto bwene Nyasaye yamanya muno akamwakholanga."""
  16,29,"“Kho, injilie mumiliango chiomumulilo kwa Jahanam, ne mumenyemwo tsinyanga tsioosi. Ne ni eshimenyo eshibi muno khubandu Abafuru.”"
  16,30,"Ne balia abaritsanga Nyasaye nibareebwa mbu: “Ni shina shia Nyasaye wenyu Omulesi yeshia?” Nibaboola mbu: “Amalayi.” Balia bakhola obulayi khushialo khuno balinyoola amalayi, ne inzu yomwikulu ni indayi po, ne inzu ya balia baria Nyasaye ni indayi muno."
  16,31,"Emikunda chilawa tawe balinjiramwo, chiburanga hakari wachio emialo, balinyoolamwo eshiabenya. Endio nilwa Nyasaye arunganga abamuriitsanga."
  16,32,"Balia aba abamalaika babafwisinjia nibekholele obulayi, (abamalaika) babolanga mbu: “Omulembe kube ninanyu. Injile mumukunda kwomwikulu khulwokhubeela kalia akamwakholanga.”"
  16,33,"Ne balindanga elindi halali Abamalaika babetsele nohomba likhuwa lia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi liboolele? Ne endio nilwabakhola balia bali imbeli wabu. Ne Nyasaye shiyabakholela obubii tawe halali abeene nibo bekholelanga obubii."
  16,34,"Mana nikabanyola amabii kabakhola, mana nibakhoyeshela kalia akabakholelanga eshiyenya meno."
  16,35,"Ne Abatsokaasi baboola mbu: “Nyasaye achamanga, shikhwakhalamile shiosishiosi habundu wuwe tawe, efwe nohomba Abapapa befu, ne shikhwakhakaanilekhwo shiosishiosi tawe halali Ye (akane).” Kho, mana endi nilwabakhola balia abali imbeli wabu. Kho, shikali khubarumwa halali okhusia butswa oburume mubulafu."
  16,36,"Ne toto khwaruma Omurumwa mubuli omukanda ababoolele mbu: “Laame Nyasaye ne mube ehale nende Shetani.” Kho, mubo balimwo ba Nyasaye yalunjisia, ne mubo balimwo bobukori bwakhoyeshela. Kho, chende khushialo mana mulolekhwo indukho yabayingasi shingala yali.”"
  16,37,"Kata norakhwo eshinani muno mbu balunjikhe, (manya mbu) Nyasaye shalunjisinjia ulia owatila okhukora tawe. Ne shibalinyoola ababahabina tawe."
  16,38,"Nabo betsuba khulira lia Nyasaye eshitsubo shiabu shia amaani mbu: “Nyasaye shalilamusia abafwa tawe.” Khulwa shina? Ni indache yayerakhwo omwene, halali Abandu abanji shibamanyile tawe."
  16,39,"Kho abenoosilie kalia akabakabukhanila, ne mbu kho Abakhayi bamanye mbu bo toto ni ababeeyi."
  16,40,"Toto likhuwa liefu khushindu shia khwenya khuboolanga butswa mbu: “Ba’’ nishiba."
  16,41,"Ne balia bawuya shichila Nyasaye nibamalile okhukholelwa obubii, toto khwitsa okhubara khushialo obulayi muno, ne omurungo kwomwikulu ni omukhongo muno, bamanyangakhwo bayie!"
  16,42,"Balia abefwila mana besikanga butswa Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  16,43,"Nafu shikhwaruma imbeli wuwo halali Abasatsa abakhwafimbulilanga obufimbuli. Kho, reebe abali nobwitsulili nikali mbu shimumanyile tawe."
  16,44,"Khubimanyisio bili habulafu nende Ebitabu. Ne khweshia amachelo kho winoosilie Abandu akeshibwa khubo, khobanyoole okhupaara."
  16,45,"Ne koo basuubilanga mbu bali nomulembe balia abakholanga ebifwanga mbu Nyasaye shiyetsa okhubasishia muliloba tawe nohomba shalabarerera eshinyasio nabo nibalamanyile tawe?"
  16,46,"Nohomba shalabatila khutsinjendo tsiabu eyi nende eyi, mana shibalanyala okhushila tawe?"
  16,47,"Nohomba mbu shalabahelesia eshinyasio muburii bwabu tawe? Toto Nyasaye wuwo ni Omuholo, Oweshisa muno."
  16,48,"Koo! Shibalolangakhwo buli bia Nyasaye yaloonga eshinikha shiabio shibotokhananga okhurula omukhono omulunji nende omukaata, ne biinamilanga Nyasaye nibihotselesiye."
  16,49,"Ne binamilanga Nyasaye bioosi bichendanga mwikulu nende khushialo, mutsisolo nende Abamalaika boosi, ne shibali abafuru tawe."
  16,50,"Baritsanga Nyasaye wabu Omulesi owuli hekulu wabu, ne bakholanga eliabalomesibungwa."
  16,51,"Ne Nyasaye yaboola mbu: “Mulabakhwo nende nyasaye babili tawe. Ye ni Nyasaye mulala butswa yenyene. Kho murie butswa esie!”"
  16,52,"Ni ebibie ebili mwikulu nende mushialo, ne idini neyiyie buli lwoosi. Koo, muritsanga ulali Nyasaye tawe?"
  16,53,"Ne emikabo chioosi cha muli ninacho ni okhurula khu Nyasaye, mana amabii nikabanyoola, niye butswa owamulililanga."
  16,54,"Mana nabarusiliaho obubii obo, awo sa, omukanda mulala mwinywe kukakhula okhumutsokaasia Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  16,55,"Khobakhaye ebiakhwabahelesia. Kho, mwikhoye. Mulitsa okhumanya."
  16,56,"Ne ebuleka webindu biakhubakabile babishilanga balia kata balamanyile tawe. Toto mulirebwa kalia koosi akamwachikhanga."
  16,57,"Ne barererangao Nyasaye Abana abakhana. Nyasaye ni Omutswenufu ehale nende ako, nabo beyenyelanga ababachama."
  16,58,"Ne mulala wabu naboolelwa amakhuwa kokhwibula omwana omukhana, obweni bwaye bumaliyanga ne yetsula nende eshibeela."
  16,59,"Yefisa mubandu khulwokhubolelwa amakhuwa amabii kabolelwe. Yereba mbu: 'Amenye ninaye nende tsisoni nohomba amuyabile mwiloba?' Manya mbu ni obubii muno obo obwababusinjia."
  16,60,"Ne balia balasuubilanga mwikulu tawe, bali nende ifwani imbii, naye Nyasaye niye weyifuma yoluyali muno, naye niwa Amaani, Owamachesi muno."
  16,61,"Ne Nyasaye abukulilanga Abandu obubii khububii bwabu, shiyakhaleshelekhwo isolo yosiyosi khushialo tawe. Halali ababikhanga okhula ebise biarebwaho. Ne ebise biabu nibiliula, shibalishinda isandala tawe nohomba shibaliiyungubasia tawe."
  16,62,"Ne bahelesinjia Nyasaye ebindu biabasinya, ne tsinimi tsiabu tsiboolanga obubeyi mbu bo balanyoola amalayi. Toto abo babishilwa omulilo, ne toto balilekhwamwo."
  16,63,"Nditsuba khu Nyasaye mbu toto efwe khwaruma (Abarumwa) mumikanda chiaranjilila imbeli wuwo, halali Shetani yabaronela ebikhole biabu. Kho, olwalelo ye niye omwitsa wabu. Nabo bali nende eshinyasio eshilulu."
  16,64,"Ne shikhwakhwishilia Eshitabu halali obenosilie kalia akabakabukhanangamwo, ne shibe obulunjifu nende tsimbabaasi khubandu basuubilanga."
  16,65,"Ne Nyasaye yeshinjia amatsi okhurula mwikulu, ni khuko alamusia liloba nilimalilenje okhufwa. Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko khubandu bawulilanga."
  16,66,"Ne toto mutsisolo mulimwo nende ameeko amakhongo. Khubanywesinjia khubilia bili mutsinda tsiatsio hakari wa amasingo nende amatsayi karulangao amabeele amalafu amalayi khubakanywetsanga."
  16,67,"Ne khubiamo bietsitende nende tsizabibu, mukasinjiamwo fiokhumeesia nende omukabo omulayi. Toto mu ako khulimwo nende ameeko khubandu bekhonyelanga obwongo."
  16,68,"Ne Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi yafimbulila inzushi mbu: “Wikasilie tsinzu mubikulu, nende khumisala nende mubilia ebiabombakhanga.’’"
  16,69,"Mana olie buli khushiamo, ne obure khutsinjila tsia Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi etsiakholwa tsinyangu. Shilarula mutsinda tsiatsio eshinywebwa shiobukondo bwaukhane, mukari washio khulimwo nende obuwonia khubandu.” Toto mukano khulimwo nende ameeko khubandu baparanga."
  16,70,"Nyasaye niye wabaloonga mana khandi abafwisinjia. Ne mwinywe balimwo bayindilanga bahebwa obulamu oburambi boola khulubaka olubi, bakorwa buli eshindu olunyuma lwokhuba abamanyi. Toto Nyasaye niye Omumanyi po, Omunyali muno."
  16,71,"Ne Nyasaye yaninia ekulu abandi mwinywe okhushila abandi khumikabo. Ne balia baninibwa shibakalusinjia omukabo kwabu khubalia abemikhono chiabu emilunji chiatila, kho babe nashilala mumikabo echo tawe. Koo, emikabo chia Nyasaye ni chio cha bakhayanga?"
  16,72,"Ne Nyasaye niye wabalonjela abakhasi okhurulana ninanyu, ne nabanyalila okhunyoola okhurula khubakhasi abo abana nende abetsukhulu, mana nabakabila ebindu ebilayi. Kho mana basuubilanga akalali katoto ne bakhayanga tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye?"
  16,73,"Ne balekhanga Nyasaye nibalaama abalakhabahelesia omukabo kwosikwosi tawe, okhurula mwikulu nohomba khushialo ne babula obunyali bwa shiosishiosi tawe."
  16,74,"Mulachelasia Nyasaye tawe. Toto Nyasaye yamanya nanyu shimumanyile tawe."
  16,75,"Nyasaye abachelasilia Abasatsa babili, mulala khubo ni omusumba omurumwa owuli hasi womwami wuwe, owulanyala shiosishiosi tawe; nende ulia owakhwakaba omukabo kurula khwifwe, mana naye arusinjia khumukabo oko mubwifisi nende mubwang’ang’u. Koo, bakhaba nashilala? Okhwitsomibwa khwoosi ni khwa Nyasaye, halali abanji mubo shibamanyile tawe."
  16,76,"Ne Nyasaye abachelasilia Abandu babili, mulala wabu ni omutimbe shanyala shiosishiosi tawe, naye ni omusiko khumwami wuwe, wosiwosi wamulinjisia, sharera obulayi bwosibwosi tawe. Koo, uno yakhaba nashilala nende ulia ulomesinjia obulunjifu, naye ali khunjila ingololofu?"
  16,77,"Ne nika Nyasaye butswa, akalalolekha komwikulu nende kokhushialo. Ne likhuwa lieyindukho lili butswa shinga okhumotiamotia tsimoni, nohomba ni ahambi muno. Toto Nyasaye ni Omunyali muno wabuli eshindu."
  16,78,"Nyasaye yabarusia mutsinda tsiabanyinenywe nimulamanyile shiosishiosi tawe. Ne nabahelesia tsimbulililo nende tsindolelo nende emioyo kho munyoole okhupa orio."
  16,79,"Koo! Shibalolangakhwo amayoni shinga kehotselesinjia mumuya tawe? Abulawo ukatilanga halali Nyasaye. Toto mu ako kalimwo ameeko khubandu basuubilanga."
  16,80,"Ne Nyasaye yabakholela tsinzu tsienyu okhuba eshimenyo. Ne nabanyalila (okhukasia) tsinzu khumaselo ketsisolo, akamunyoolanga mbu ni amangu khubise bioluchendo lwenyu, nende ebise biokhuwulukha khwenyu.. nende khubukoya bwatsio nende amabaa katsio nende obukuya bwatsio, ebiamukasilinjia ebindu biokhwikhonyela khubise sa."
  16,81,"Ne Nyasaye khubindu biayabalonjela yabakholela eshinikha, ne nabakasilia eshimenyo mufikulu, ne nabakholela tsingubo tsibashinganga okhurulana nende obutundumu ubunji, nende tsingubo tsiebichuma etsibashinganga mumiero chienyu. Endio nilwa abetsusilinjia tsimbabaasi tsitsie kho munyoole okhumwilekhulila."
  16,82,"Ne nibaloba, shikali khwiwe halali okhusya khuli hafulafu."
  16,83,"Bamanya emikabo chia Nyasaye mana bachikhayanga. Ne abanji mubo ni abakhayi."
  16,84,"Ne inyanga yakhulibuusia buli mumukanda omuloli, ne abakhayi shibalichamilwa nohomba shibalileshelwa okhusaba eshileshelo tawe."
  16,85,"Ne balia abakhola tsimbi olwabalilola eshinyasio, shibalitutuyilibwa eshinyasio esho tawe, nohomba shibalihelesibwa ebise bindi tawe."
  16,86,"Ne balia batsokaasia Nyasaye olwa balilola abatsokaasi babu, baliboola mbu: “Nyasaye wefu Omulesi, bano nibo abatsokaasi befu, abakhwalamanga habundu wuwo.” Nabo balibasukunila likhuwa nibaboolela mbu: “Toto enywe muli ababeyi.”"
  16,87,"Ne inyanga eyo balilekhulila Nyasaye, ne akabachikhanga kalibakora."
  16,88,"Balia bakhaya mana nibekalila (abandu) injila ya Nyasaye, khulibametela eshinyasio hekulu weshinyasio shingala abeene bakholanga amabii."
  16,89,"Ne inyanga yakhulirusia buli mumukanda omuloli khubo okhurulana ninabo, ne wesi khukhurere obe omuloli khu bano. Ne khwakhwishilia Eshitabu shino eshiboolanga buli eshindu, nashio ni obulunjifu nende tsimbabaasi, nende obusangali khubasalamu."
  16,90,"Toto Nyasaye alomesinjia okhukhola obuleeng’afu, nende okhukhola obulayi, nende okhuhelesia abeekho, ne akania eshifwolo nende okhukhola tsimbi. Abebaalilanga kho munyale okhwitsulila."
  16,91,"Ne mukhole indakano ya Nyasaye nimulakana, ne mulafunaka ibitsubo bienyu tawe nimumalile okhubiraho naamaani tawe, ne nimumalile okhukhola Nyasaye okhuba omuloli wenyu. Toto Nyasaye amanyile kamukholanga."
  16,92,"Ne mulaba shinga Omukhasi ulia owateta olusi lulwe ebitonye ebitonye, nilumalilenje okhuba oluumu. Mukholanga ebitsubo bienyu okhuba injila yokhukatania. Khulwa okhuba mbu omukanda mulala kwa Abandu kuli nende amaani okhushila omukanda kwa Abandu bandi. Toto Nyasaye abatemanga munjila eyo. Ne toto alibaboolela inyanga yeyindukho akamwawukhanilanga."
  16,93,"Ne Nyasaye yenyanga, yakhabakholele okhuba omukanda mulala butswa. Halali akosinjia owayenya, ne alunjisinjia owayenya. Ne toto mulirebwa khukalia koosi kamwakholanga."
  16,94,"Ne mulakhola okhwitsuba khwenyu okhuba khwokhukatania hakari wenyu tawe. Eshilenje shiletsa shiarerekha nishibeele nishimalile okhwema obulai muno, mana mupile amabii kenyu khulwa okhwikalila injila ya Nyasaye, mwanyoola eshinyasio eshikhongo."
  16,95,"Ne mulakula shiobukusi obutiti khumalako ka Nyasaye tawe. Eshili ewa Nyasaye nishio eshilayi khwinywe, nikali mbu mwakhamanya."
  16,96,"Ebiamuli ninabio biliwa, ne ebili wa Nyasaye nibo bilitong’a, ne toto efwe khulihelesia balia befwila omurungo kwabu khumalayi kabu kabakholanga."
  16,97,"Yesiyesi ukhola amalayi abe omusatsa nohomba omukhasi, naye nali omusuubili, khwitsa toto okhumumenyia obulamu obulayi, ne toto khulibarunga omurungo kwabu khumalayi kabu kabakholanga."
  16,98,"Ne niwenya okhusoma Ikurani, wilinde khu Nyasaye okhurulana nende Shetani owalondwa."
  16,99,"Toto ye abula amaani khubalia basuubila, mana besikanga Nyasaye wabu Omulesi."
  16,100,"Amaani kaye kali khubalia abamwaambanga obulina, nende balia abamutsokaasinjia nende Nyasaye."
  16,101,"Ne nikhukalukhania olunyali habundu wolunyali, ne Nyasaye ni umanyile muno akayeshinjia, baboola mbu: “Ewe olisa omuchishi.” Halali abanji mubo shibamanyile tawe."
  16,102,"Boola mbu: “Roho woluyali yakeshia okhurula khu Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khubwatoto, kho katinyisie balia basuubila, ne kabe obulunjifu nende kokhurera akomwikhoyo khubasalamu."
  16,103,"Ne toto khwamanya mbu balaboola mbu: “Omundu niye umwechesinjia” ulusungo lwa ulia owabamanyinjia nilweshicheni, niluno ni olusungo lweshiarabu lwa habulafu."
  16,104,"Toto balia balasuubilanga tsinyaali tsia Nyasaye tawe, Nyasaye shabalunjisinjia tawe, ne balinyoola eshinyasio eshilulu."
  16,105,"Balia abachikhanga obubeyi ni balia abalasuubilanga ebimanyisio bia Nyasaye tawe, ne abo nibo ababeyi."
  16,106,"Ulia ukhaya Nyasaye namalilenje okhusuubila, halali ulia unichilisibwe ne omwoyo kwaye nikubunile po khubusubili, ne ulia wikulilanga eshilifu shishie obukhayi, obusinyifu bwa Nyasaye buli khubo, ne balinyoola eshinyasio eshikhongo."
  16,107,"Endio nilwokhuba mbu bo bachama obulamu bwokhushialo okhushila obulamu bwomwikulu. Ne toto Nyasaye shalunjisinjia Abandu abakhayi tawe."
  16,108,"Abo nibo aba Nyasaye yasuba emioyo chiabu nende tsimbulililo tsiabu nende tsindolelo tsiabu. Ne abo nibo abakaandala."
  16,109,"Inganakani ibulaho tawe, abo nibo balibula obukhala mwikulu."
  16,110,"Mana toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khubalia abawuya nibakhasandibwa, mana nibalwana mana nibesumilisia, toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olunyuma lwa ako ni Omulesheli muno, Owetsimbabaasi po."
  16,111,"Inyanga yabuli omundu alitsa okhwikomelela omwene, ne buli omundu alirungwa mubwitsufu akayakholanga, ne shibalikholelwa obubii tawe."
  16,112,"Nyasaye abachelasilinjia olukongo lwali nende omulembe nende obwihotselefu, omukabo kwalwo kwalwitsilanga mubunji okhurulila buli elubeka. Halali nilukhaya tsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye, mana Nyasaye nalupilia eshifwalo shieyinzala nende oburi khulwokhubeela kalia akabakholanga."
  16,113,"Ne Omurumwa yabetsela okhurula mubo, mana nibamuyingasia, mana eshinyasio nishiboolela nibalibo abeene bekholela obubii."
  16,114,"Ne mulie khubilia bia Nyasaye abahelesiyie, ebiamwachamilwa ebilayi, ne mukhupe orio khutsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye, toto nimuli mbu mumulamanga Ye sa."
  16,115,"Yabakania okhulia shifwile, nende amalasile, nende inyama yeyimbitsi, nende shisinzilwe nishilarumbulilwekho elira lia Nyasaye tawe. Halali ulia unichililisibwa bilali okhufienya nohomba okhubura eshichelo tawe, awo toto Nyasaye ni omunji wobulesheli, Owetsimbabaasi muno."
  16,116,"Ne mulaboola khububeyi bwetsinimi tsienyu mbu: “Shino shiafuchililwa ne shino shiakanibwa.” Muletsa mwachishila Nyasaye obubeyi. Toto bachishilanga Nyasaye obubeyi shibalibura tawe."
  16,117,"Omwikhoyo mutiti butwsa, ne balinyoola eshinyasio eshikhongo muno."
  16,118,"Ne Abayahudi khwabakania akakhubakaniile khale awo, ne shikhwabakholela obubii tawe, halali bo abeene nibekholela obubii."
  16,119,"Mana toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khubalia bakholanga obubii khubulamanya mana nibekanila nibakhakhola ako, mana nibakhola amalayi, toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi olunyuma lwa ako ni Omunji wokhuleshela, Omunji westimbabaasi."
  16,120,"Toto Ibrahim yali Omwimilisi, Omwihotselefu khu Nyasaye, Omutswenufu, ne shiyali mubatsokaasi tawe."
  16,121,"Yali omukhupi wa orio khutsimbabaasi tsia Nyasaye. Mana namwawula ne namulunjisia khunjila ingololofu."
  16,122,"Mana nikhumuhelesia mushialo amalayi, naye toto mwikulu aliba mubandu abalayi."
  16,123,"Mana nikhukhufimbulila mbu: “Loonda emilukha chia Ibrahim omulunjifu, ne shiyali mubatsokaasi tawe.”"
  16,124,"Toto Jumamosi yarebwaho khubalia bakabukhanamwo khuyo, ne toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi, alikhalaka eshina hakari wabu inyanga yeyindukho khukalia akabakabukhanangamwo."
  16,125,"Langa khunjila ya Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi mumachesi, nende amachelo amalayi, ne olomalome nabo munjila indayi muno. Toto Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi amanyile muno ulia wakora ehale nende injila yiyie, ne amanyile muno balia abalunjikha."
  16,126,"Ne nimurunga imoongo, runge ebihelana nende ebia mukholelwe amabii. Ne nimwifwila, toto awo nobulayi khubalia abefwilanga."
  16,127,"Ne wifwile. Okhwifwila khukhwo khulaba halali khulwa Nyasaye butswa. Ne olabeelela shichila bo tawe. Ne olaba mubunyakhani shichila kabatutanga tawe."
  16,128,"Toto Nyasaye ali halala nende balia bamuria, nende balia abakholanga amalayi."
